<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Gospel khuolzin khawilama chieh ding na him?
 Nang hun ngaia dangchak sang tamtak aum tai;
 En zinga mulo leh, za zinga zalo ten;
 Na nasep hukdamna a ngak zing ui.

[V2]
 Muol leh tang sang lele chieh ding ka hi,
 Lalpa thupiek zuilo thei ka hi puoi;
 A hehpih nan ei sawl ka chamlo in,
 Lal na ka sep ding him ahi.

[V3]
 2. Sietna suok in mi sangzatam thim nuoi ah um,
 Kalvari suohchakna nisuoh lam helo in;
 Gawtmun lamah din a them lungmuong Setan in,
 A chieh zing ui Aw Gospel sam meng in.

[V4]
 3. Gospel sapna pawm nuomlo te cheng cheng chuvang,
 Kah leh hagiel na thuok unau kumsawt chan in;
 Zie chun kisik mahleu ngaihdam hi ta puon au,
 A chung un a kumsawt thiemloh chuta.

[V5]
 4. Aw suohpihte Gospel sapna pawmkin meng un,
 Gospel laktoh nani Rapture ni anai tai;
 Hukdam chate cheng chu chung gam ah cheng unau,
 Chawldam tan au Hallelujah tiin.</lyrics>
<title>&quot;Muol leh Tangsang Lele&quot;</title>
<hymn_number>327</hymn_number>
<author>Rev. Douzapao</author>
</song>